Each character decides on their tasks:
‚Ä¢	The Guardians of the Cocoon Kingdom will measure tree heights and observe the extent of plant cover.
‚Ä¢	The Crystal Moths will record humidity and temperature data.
‚Ä¢	The Chrysalis Shamans will collect soil samples to analyze nutrient levels.
