The team sets off into the forest, using their specialized tools to gather essential data:
‚Ä¢	Crystal Moths flutter through the air, measuring temperature and humidity with precision.
‚Ä¢	Guardians of the Cocoon Kingdom measure the height of towering trees, jotting down their findings in the Data Log.
‚Ä¢	Chrysalis Shamans dig into the earth, collecting soil samples to test for nutrients.
