‚Ä¢	The Quantum Butterflies compare their measurements with GLOBE datasets accessed through GLOBE.gov. They look for correlations between humidity levels and tree growth.
‚Ä¢	Caterpillar Queens encourage the team to think critically about the data, asking, ‚ÄúDoes the air quality affect the health of the trees?‚Äù
Step 6: Draw Conclusions
As they analyze the data, the team discovers that:
‚Ä¢	Areas with lower humidity correlate with stunted tree growth.
‚Ä¢	Soil samples reveal a lack of essential nutrients, confirming the Chrysalis Shamans‚Äô concerns.
Step 7: Communicate Results
With their findings in hand, the team prepares a comprehensive report:
‚Ä¢	Caterpillar Queens lead the presentation, showcasing how their data compares with the historical GLOBE datasets.
‚Ä¢	They highlight the importance of restoring moisture levels and enriching the soil to promote healthier growth in the forest.
